WEBVTT

00:03:58.600 --> 00:04:01.216
Mwaka wa shule Marekani ni miezi 10 tu.

00:04:01.240 --> 00:04:03.856
Kama watoto watapoteza miezi 5 
ya kujifunza kila mwaka

00:04:03.880 --> 00:04:05.360
hiyo ni nusu ya elimu yao.

00:04:06.120 --> 00:04:07.320
Nusu.

00:04:08.080 --> 00:04:11.340
Kama watoto wangekuwa shule 
kipindi cha kiangazi, wasingerudi nyuma,

00:04:12.000 --> 00:04:14.600
lakini shule ya kiangazi iliyozoeleka 
imeundwa vibaya.

00:04:14.920 --> 00:04:16.976
Kwa watoto inaonekana kama adhabu,

00:04:17.000 --> 00:04:19.040
na kwa walimu inaonekana kama uyaya.

00:04:20.320 --> 00:04:24.336
Lakini tunatarajia vipi walimu wakuu 
kutekeleza programu madhubuti ya kiangazi

00:04:24.360 --> 00:04:26.816
ikiwa mwaka wa shule unaisha 
juma la mwisho la Juni

00:04:26.840 --> 00:04:29.220
na shule ya kiangazi inaanza 
juma moja tu baadaye?

00:04:29.960 --> 00:04:32.530
Yaani hakuna wakati wa kutosha 
kupata watu sahihi